4.5 Memanipulasi Gambar

#Manipulating Image
img_neg = max(image) - image
display( img_neg )
## Only the first frame of the image stack is displayed.
## To display all frames use 'all = TRUE'.

img_comb = combine(
  image,
  image + 0.3,
  image * 2,
  image ^ 0.5
)
display(img_comb, all=TRUE)

img_t = transpose(image)
display( img_t )
## Only the first frame of the image stack is displayed.
## To display all frames use 'all = TRUE'.

4.6 Seni, Pemrosesan Gambar, dan Representasi Spektral Sinyal

4.6.1 Menyiapkan Gambar

library(EBImage)
images <- readImage("C:/Users/herib/OneDrive/Pictures/Al-Qur_an-Biru.jpg")
display(images, method = "raster", all = TRUE)

4.6.2 Intensity Histogram

hist(images)

4.6.3 Generate negative image

img_neg <- max(images) - images
display( img_neg )

4.6.4 crop and threshold

img_crop <- images
img_thresh <- img_crop > 0.55
display(img_thresh)

4.6.5 Low-pass Filter/smooth

w <- makeBrush(size = 31, shape = 'gaussian', sigma = 5)
img_flo <- filter2(images, w)
display(img_flo)

4.6.6 High-pass filtering Laplace Filter/Edge detection

fhi <- matrix(1, nrow = 3, ncol = 3)
fhi[2, 2] <- -7
img_fhi <- filter2(images, fhi)
display(img_fhi)

4.6.7 Denoising

img_median <- medianFilter(images, size=5, cacheSize=20000)
display(img_median)

4.6.8 Segmentation

grayimage <- channel(images,"gray")
threshold <- otsu(grayimage)
CC_th <- combine( mapply(function(frame, th) frame > th, 
                         getFrames(images), 
                         threshold, SIMPLIFY=FALSE) )
display(CC_th, all=TRUE)

disc <- makeBrush(51, "disc")
disc <- disc/sum(disc)
offset <- 0.0001
CC_bg <- filter2(images, disc)
CC_th <- images < CC_bg + offset
display(CC_th, all=TRUE)

4.6.9 Watershed segmentation

nmask <- watershed(distmap(CC_th), tolerance=5, ext=20)
display(colorLabels(nmask), all=TRUE)

4.6.10 Voronoi image tesselation

voronoiExamp <- propagate(x = nmask, seeds = nmask, lambda = 0.001)
voronoiPaint <- colorLabels (voronoiExamp)
display(voronoiPaint, all=TRUE)

CC <- rgbImage(green=2.0*CC_bg, blue=img_median, red=voronoiPaint[ , , , 1])
display(CC, all = TRUE)

ctmask = opening(img_fhi<0.6, makeBrush(5, shape='disc'))
cmask = propagate(img_fhi, seeds=nmask, mask=ctmask)
display(ctmask, all=TRUE)

ctmask = opening(img_fhi>0.1, makeBrush(5, shape='disc'))
cmask = propagate(img_fhi, seeds=nmask, mask=ctmask)
display(ctmask, all=TRUE)

segmented = paintObjects(channel(cmask,"gray"), images, col='#ff00ff')
segmented = paintObjects(channel(ctmask,"gray"), segmented, col='#ffff00')
display(segmented, all=TRUE)
